Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这栋房子里只有我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有我看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动…了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我已经不太害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得那大概是神仙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里一直都是夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:03:01.16,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,0)\p1\c&HAA90A6&}m 0 0 l -500 0 l -500 100 l 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:03:01.16,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,0)\pos(235,252)}壶天之星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 娃娃不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又藏起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天又是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空的那一边是哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里一个人也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是因为大家都到天空的那一边去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样 星星在小小的天空里闪烁的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像从前也在别处见过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的一切都很美 很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就懒得去回想其他了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这房子真大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 下次再增加一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 瑞穗 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在和小泉玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么连你都还在说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你娘又找了奇怪的人来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 小泉肯定是被人掳走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爹我一定会找到她的 你就别再做这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我…真的…看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井底什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银古先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样了 小泉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 时间不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 你女儿确实活在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是你们彼此接触不到对方罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我每次能和她同步的时间很短
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果待久了 我也会忘记回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越是适应那里的人就越会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我会再和她同步试试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉就在这房子里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 虽然你可能看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我的娃娃总会被拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉就总是这样 明明她自己也有娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我现在也会把娃娃藏起来和她玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:09:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是受你母亲之讬来带你回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你掉进家后山的古井里 来到「这边」了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么 我才不知道什么井
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你很适应这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你的人所在的地方 才是你的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在那片天空的另一边等你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天做好饭菜等你回来的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏起娃娃和你玩耍的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不是你该待的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就直接动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 瑞穗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井底有星星在发光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 有那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 我们回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里玩会挨骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉 来玩娃娃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 星星变少了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 我把娃娃借你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 反正你马上就会叫我还
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我送给你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 看得见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 星星又变少了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉 你在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只找到了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 我看到小泉是从这里掉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别胡说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞穗 你又和小泉吵架了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以小泉离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉肯定在别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 娘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信银古先生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果井里冒烟了 就向着井底喊话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 看来还有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我会再和小泉同步一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可能失去记忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过只要想起来 她还是能够回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 时间有限
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果来不及 我会从那边强行接通这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备我已经做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 就能从这里把声音传给小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉 小泉 小泉 ……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞穗 娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是…小泉的声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在说「我在这里」…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从家那边传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁在这儿生火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子星星也恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 数量比之前少了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫「井星」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一口井位于光脉这种生命之源的奔流相撞的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就偶尔会出现这种现象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 就像是光脉相撞所产生的火星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果接触得太多 就会变成像你这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星的数量之所以减少 或许是因为光脉的位置发生偏移了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 这都是和你无关的遥远世界的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该和这里告别了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 让开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爹 我不会再来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再让我担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爹 你这是做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让井里的神仙能换换气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地底是否寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否痛苦 是否可怕 是否寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地底深处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是清净的水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:21:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与无数繁星的住处
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 碧水
